Packages that use VariableConfiguration
Package
Description
com.pandora.chemistry.interfaces
This package contains interfaces related to biogeochemistry in freshwater systems, specifically focusing on PANDORA chemistry.
com.pandora.config
The com.pandora.config.species package contains classes and interfaces related to the configuration and management of biogeochemical species in PANDORA.
com.pandora.config.species
The com.pandora.config.species package contains classes and interfaces related to the configuration and management of biogeochemical species in the Pandora biogeochemical model.
com.pandora.config.species.abstractions
The com.pandora.config.species.abstractions package contains abstractions for representing biogeochemical species in a freshwater context.
